1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,700
The mind fails when you need it most.

2
00:00:03,700 --> 00:00:07,200
Your goal will be to remember Greek letters and colors.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:12,200
To do that, you will use your tokens, the terminals, and the buttons.

4
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:15,900
At the start, you will see your token numbers on screen.

5
00:00:15,900 --> 00:00:18,700
Look carefully, because they will disappear.

6
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:22,500
And in their place, a Greek letter in a specific color will appear.

7
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:25,800
Take your token to the terminal with that same letter.

8
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,700
Then press the button of the same color.

9
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:33,300
If even one person makes a mistake, the phase will reset.

10
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:36,700
It seems simple, only at first.

11
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,500
Each new phase will demand more memory.

12
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:40,500
Good luck.
